---
title: Sumac-Paprika Steak with Tomato Chickpea Mash and Roasted Cauliflower
description: Steak is pretty good, but here we’ve made it even better with the delicious peppery tang of sumac! Our top tip on cooking steak is to get the pan roasting hot before laying in the steak … when we say hot, WE MEAN HOT
